Just because a man can cause more physical pain does not mean that we should let it be okay for our women to run wild and not learn to how to control their anger and for that matter, their emotions as well. (I am saying our women here like our baby girls. Our children.) If we don't control it from the beginning they will grow up with this same attitude towards our men.
Feminism isn't bad if what you are fighting for are equal rights, but when it turns to putting men down and abusing them physically or even emotionally then that is a problem. Think of your children. Would you be okay with some bi+C# hitting him and cutting any body parts off just cause she was angry or because he wanted to leave her? That's BS. Other people might think it's funny but it's not. These women should be in jail doing hard time and if we just let it go on blindly things will never change.
